column5: I was going to get her mounted to match the 15" I already have mounted to make book ends but had no means of preserving the fish, would of been a waste so back she went.
Monster! Get a photo replica made, that’s what I did for my 14.5 inch perch and the big bass my son and I caught last summer.
Probably in the mouth Good one, LMAO.
Take lots of measurements and get replica made. Fish goes back to make more monster babies and you have a keepsake

Take lots of measurements and get replica made. Fish goes back to make more monster babies and you have a keepsake I second that, I’ve done that with a huge perch and have a huge bass being made right now.
